 src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/241504/241504.3_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2F241504%2F241504.3_.png&h=20c89450&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\r <br />\r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r <br />\r<em><span class=\"small\">上述資料更新日期：2020/12/2<br />\rP.S. 呢個唔係五毛 LIST，係戇鳩 LIST，可以畀大家認識到比較特別嘅會員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></em>"},{"pid":"10b497c30ad92692a790da43a97e6ffae6769d5c","tid":2318943,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T19:04:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Flihkg_on9_list&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=e23b5d7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">歡迎光臨 LIHKG on9 list<br />\n大家認為係五毛分化撚等等會員<br />\n如非必要一律視為戇鳩仔<br />\n以方便整理本名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">本名單最近更新內容：<br />\n- 新增部份會員嘅留言備份連結 (以免被 del 留言無哂證據)<br />\n- 新增 [img] 功能整合已上載的留言圖片連結方便狙擊</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4xjDjR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4xjDjR.gif&h=335cbd9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">*</span></strong></span> 本名單現已支援由髀加蕉 (#23094) 巴打編寫的會員標籤功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ArJRKK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ArJRKK.gif&h=874afd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前僅適用於電腦和 Android 版瀏覽器：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/oqmHmzX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/oqmHmzX</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZdCwSLv44U0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZdCwSLv44U0&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=883a4ded\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZdCwSLv44U0</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><em><span class=\"small\">最近更新日期：2020/12/8 1:32:58</span></em></span>"},{"pid":"dd8df5b485d0ee8a5aa3b83f0df4c1d2e732d55b","tid":2318943,"uid":147031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T19:12:07.000Z","msg":"無人講未你講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272ad10f174a352eb5ca81260889db6f4b67a85f","tid":2318943,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T00:25:58.000Z","msg":"生果music 幾乎冇第三方硬件同軟件用到，Network Streamer 冇，Linux Audiophile 冇，講音質有排唔到佢，講平佢唔係最平，講好用唔見得<br />\n<br />\n嘥鳩氣產品嚟"},{"pid":"6577532703949fbde3e45402107a3afada799f8b","tid":2318943,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"冇人講咪你講囉我屌你老母臭閪<br />\n你講唔撚得架？好撚委屈你架？其他人開post講撚咗先我係咪又可以屌你唔撚講先？<br />\n係咪覺得冇人講，自己就好撚有優越感，開post就係都要加多一兩句屌人先得？<br />\n乜撚嘢話題都實有第一個人講架啦，係咪個撚個開post都要屌人「ＸＸ都冇人講」？<br />\n好聲好氣唔撚得嘅，係咪以為個撚個都廿四小時mon撚住乜柒都知？<br />\n呢啲戇鳩仔，完全喺到消磨所有人嘅耐性，助長負面情緒。<br />\n屌你老母我真係唔撚知有件咁嘅事啊嘛，碌碌下post無撚啦啦畀你屌，唔撚知唔撚得架？<br />\n冇人知冇人提咁咪你提話人知囉我屌你老母，你知又唔撚講其他人唔知又可以點撚樣講啊？<br />\n接收資訊嗰個一定要畀發放資訊嗰個屌架？<br />\n係咪你細個你老竇教你寫字嗰陣一路教一路屌你老母先教到你呢啲撚樣出嚟？<br />\n屌你老母臭閪谷鳩氣"},{"pid":"9f1cd40556a2df1c82e87711bb787758173ac005","tid":2318943,"uid":248695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾音質"},{"pid":"5ae0808b3f3543048d63b0fb72aa545a1d2f0f40","tid":2318943,"uid":297329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb75fe32541862d200c5b097ef45f644647501a2","tid":2318943,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"1d965d2268f990eece10f1670b2af