之前有動態歌詞班Spotify傻閪都好似發現新大陸咁。。。<br />\n<br />\n仲有Spotify 而家係咪冇得互相follow d friend 睇人聽咩？<br />\n最後講成個設計介面點都係Apple Music 靚好多啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgRmjUo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgRmjUo.png&h=5e13e1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDMNfsN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDMNfsN.png&h=8f133587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iP4yVsP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiP4yVsP.png&h=b960600a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LjX417Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjX417Q.png&h=81eac54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHckAsR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHckAsR.png&h=14d44e5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74c0ea9e4b9eedf84acf022cac2309e4c455ef32","tid":2318943,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28c39bd2a885851234619e0ce2b966530f724a2b","tid":2318943,"uid":127244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"272ad10f174a352eb5ca81260889db6f4b67a85f","tid":2318943,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T00:25:58.000Z","msg":"生果music 幾乎冇第三方硬件同軟件用到，Network Streamer 冇，Linux Audiophile 冇，講音質有排唔到佢，講平佢唔係最平，講好用唔見得<br />\n<br />\n嘥鳩氣產品嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T05:14:21.000Z","msg":"唔明邊忽晒鳩氣喎⋯⋯成個介面排列有序清晰列咗出嚟我最近聽咗乜嘢朋友聽緊乜嘢有乜嘢新歌乜嘢風格又有乜嘢推介，xx 心情又有咩推介<br />\n<br />\n你講嗰啲都唔係問題嚟嘅<br />\n仲有乜嘢Linux正常人都唔會用到<br />\n<br />\n大部份人都係配合macOS iMac /MacBook  tvOS ( Apple TV  iOS + AirPod / HomePod 咁用咖啦<br />\n<br />\n我見經常有人用Spotify同Apple Music 比較就決定再入去究竟睇吓有乜嘢好<br />\n因為我最後一次用Spotify 都已經係八年前...<br />\n發現Spotify唔單止冇進步甚至可以講係退化，難怪Apple Music 搶咗咁多客變咗全球第二多人用<br />\n<br />\nApple Music 淨係電台都已經大把野玩，NY/SF/ London 三個studio每日無間斷製造新節目 ，經常請唔同明星藝人上去主持電台節目已經其他冇得比啦，<br />\n<br />\n基本上一督開就已經有嘢聽。好多時連自己原